                        <p><b>Laboratory Works:</b></p><p>The laboratory work includes developing E-commerce applications. The students are highly encouraged to use server side and client side scripting for developing the applications with categories, shopping carts, payment gateways. Students can also use open source ecommerce CMS frameworks and configure them to simulate e-commerce systems. The laboratory work for e-comerce optimization includes SEO tools like Google Analytics, Facebook Analytics,Twitter Analytics etc. Students can also implement basic recommendation system in the e- commerce systems.</p>
